# Code owners for qeet-identity.
#
# Lines later in the file take precedence. Owners listed for a path are
# automatically requested as reviewers when a PR touches that path.
#
# Syntax: <pattern> <owner1> <owner2> ...
# Replace @qeetgroup/* team handles with real teams or @-handles when known.

